How do I update this listing?




                                             Polygon Management Ltd. is based out of Grand Cayman.   Their last reported 13F filing for Q1 2017 included $533,088,000 in managed 13F securities
    and a top 10 holdings concentration of 67.45%. Polygon Management Ltd.'s largest holding is Jazz Pharma Plc with shares held of 31,330,000.   WhaleWisdom has at least 20 13Fs and  9 13D/G filings in our database for Polygon Management Ltd.. 
                                           














